{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2819","heading":"Strategy and assessment with respect to non-operational, underutilized, and other Department of Defense facilities: assessments of historical significance","label":"2819 Strategy and assessment with respect to non-operational, underutilized, and other Department of Defense facilities: assessments of historical significance","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptIV/ch169/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextSection 2838 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2024, referred to in subsecs. (a)(1) and (e)(2)(C)(i), is , which is set out as a note preceding .section 2838 of Pub. L. 118–31section 2851 of this title","Amendments2025—Subsec. (e). inserted “the” before “congressional defense committees”.Pub. L. 119–60"],"amendments":["Amendments2025—Subsec. (e). inserted “the” before “congressional defense committees”.Pub. L. 119–60"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Strategy for Demolition","label":"a .—Strategy for Demolition","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"are in poor or failing condition under the uniform index developed under section 2838 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2024 ();Public Law 118–31","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"are not in operational use; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"such Secretary determines are underutilized.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Assessment of Certain Maintenance Costs","label":"b .—Assessment of Certain Maintenance Costs","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"are not in operational use; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"such Secretary determines are underutilized.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":".—Required Consideration","label":"c .—Required Consideration","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In determining whether a facility is underutilized pursuant to subsections (a) or (b), each Secretary concerned shall compare the occupancy of such facility to the total square footage of such facility.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":".—Assessments of Historic Significance","label":"d .—Assessments of Historic Significance","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is historically significant; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"will be historically significant at the end of the 25-year period beginning on the date of the completion of such assessment.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"conduct an assessment of the condition of such facility;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"make an initial determination of whether such facility will be modernized or demolished during such 25-year period; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2/C/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F2%2FC%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the results of the assessment under subparagraph (A); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2/C/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/2/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F2%2FC%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the initial determination required by subparagraph (B).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"If, during the course of any assessment of a facility described in paragraph (1), the Secretary concerned changes a determination with respect to the historic significance of the facility or plans of such Secretary to modernize or demolish the facility, such Secretary shall revise the information submitted to the applicable digital facilities management system pursuant to subparagraph (C) of paragraph (2).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":".—Annual Briefing","label":"e .—Annual Briefing","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the strategy required by subsection (a); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the results of the assessments required by subsections (b) and (d).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a summary of the existing authorities of each Secretary concerned to demolish the facilities covered by such strategy;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a plan to implement such strategy; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2/C/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F2%2FC%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the inventory of facilities in poor or failing condition under the uniform index developed under section 2838 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2024 (); andPublic Law 118–31","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2/C/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2819/e/2/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2819%2Fe%2F2%2FC%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the total cost to the United States to maintain the facilities covered by the assessment required by subsection (b) of such section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}]}
